{"parse":{"title":"National Ex-Slave Mutual Relief, Bounty and Pension Association","pageid":49417702,"revid":799089818,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Callie_House.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0a/Callie_House.jpg/200px-Callie_House.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"262\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0a/Callie_House.jpg/300px-Callie_House.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0a/Callie_House.jpg/400px-Callie_House.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"696\" data-file-height=\"912\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Callie_House.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Co-Founder of the MRB&amp;PA Callie House (1861-1928).</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>National Ex-Slave Mutual Relief, Bounty and Pension Association</b> (MRB&amp;PA) was an organization founded for the purpose of obtaining pensions for former slaves from the Federal government as compensation and reparations for their unpaid labor and suffering. Founded in 1896 and chartered in 1898 in Nashville, Tennessee, the organization was founded by former slaves <a href=\"/wiki/Callie_House\" title=\"Callie House\">Callie House</a> and <a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Isaiah_H._Dickerson&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Isaiah H. Dickerson (page does not exist)\">Isaiah H. Dickerson</a>. According to historian Mary Frances Berry, the organization was \"the first mass reparations movement led by African Americans.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Early_history\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Early history</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Conventions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Conventions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Legislative_efforts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Legislative efforts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Relief_efforts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Relief efforts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Federal_investigations\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Federal investigations</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Decline\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Decline</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Footnotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Footnotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Further_reading\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Further reading</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Early_history\">Early history</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=National_Ex-Slave_Mutual_Relief,_Bounty_and_Pension_Association&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Early history\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"vertical-navbox nowraplinks\" style=\"float:right;clear:right;width:22.0em;margin:0 0 1.0em 1.0em;background:#f9f9f9;border:1px solid #aaa;padding:0.2em;border-spacing:0.4em 0;text-align:center;line-height:1.4em;